body:
I&#039;m just getting back into the game after a bit of a hiatus. NO MORE HONORABLE OPPONENT!? Honoring your opponents is an actual meaningful way to show your appreciation for another player&#039;s skill. It was always so nice when a player from the other team recognizes your skills and honors you for it. Why would you take that out? :P

Also, being prompted to honor a teammate at the end of every game is annoying. If I feel like they did well I will honor them. And what about multiple honoring? Is that just gone now?

This ain&#039;t no Overwatch {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}}
